<i>noun</i>: 탐험 [탐험] <i>verb</i>: 탐험하다 [탐험하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탐험 [탐험]</dt><br>
<dd>exploration; expedition</dd><br>
<dd>위험을 참고 견디며 어떤 곳을 찾아가서 살펴보고 조사함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of going to a location to observe and study its characteristics, often in dangerous conditions.</dd><br>
</li>
